short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Fix audio on the basis that one side(channel) is playing and the other is not, or one is louder!

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
